snippet.textDisplay:
the true REmake is the 1st REmake. One masterfully produced by the
father of survival horror, Shinji Mikami. The first REmake was
faithfully modeled after the original RE style, and did everything right
and is right, the style and gameplay of the original RE games is way
better than Over the shoulder action shooter RE2imagined and
RE3imagined.

A true proper RE2make and RE3make should have:

1) 2020 4K UHD Pre-rendered backgrounds
2) 4K UHD 3D Character Models
3) Fixed Camera Angles
4) Tank Controls
5) Original Door Opening/Closing Sequences (OG Loading screens)
6) Survival Horror

New
OTS shooter action horror RE2imagined and RE3imagined has none of the
key ingredients above. action shooter modern RE2imagined RE3imagined is
going to please the casual crowd but it will never win the hearts of
true classic RE fans.
